//*********************************************************************
//*
//* NAME: SYS1.SETUP.CNTL(MVS0060)
//*
//* DESC: INSTALL USERMOD ZP60003 TO ALLOW BLANK LINES
//*       IN IFOX00 SOURCE MODULES
